Package: recogeo
Type: Package
Title: A R package to reconcile geographies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Francesco Bailo
Maintainer: Francesco Bailo <me@francescobailo.net>
Description: It implements functions to reconcile geographies that have been 
    redrawn. It compares the geographies contained in two spatial objects and 
    based on a spatial analysis it defines a one-to-one, a one-to-many, a many-to-one 
    or a many-to-many relation among the geographies of the two spatial objects.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    sf,
    sp,
    dplyr,
    reshape2,
    ggplot2
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
